source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Package current chunk into a ZIP file (recording stays active)

Usage: bl record chunk stop [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -o, --output <output>  Output file path (default: chunk.zip)
  -v, --verbose          Enable debug logging
      --headless         Hide browser window (visible by default)
      --json             Output as JSON
  -h, --help             Print help

Examples:
  bl record chunk stop
  # Save chunk to chunk.zip

  bl record chunk stop -o part1.zip
